## Goal

Validate the three pain points HiveMind asked us to test against the Christoph persona — cognitive load, system fragmentation, and lack of a single trustworthy source of company knowledge — through real conversations with working professionals.

## Sample

6 working professionals, recruited through team networks. Per the student handbook, **no students** — only people with real workplace experience.

